==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polyembryony
<hw>Pol`y*em"bry*o*ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Poly-</er>, and <er>Embryo</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
production of two or more embryos in one seed, due either to the
existence and fertilization of more than one embryonic sac or to the
origination of embryos outside of the embryonic sac.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polyfoil</ent>⟦br⟧
